name: Silver Hummingbird Pin - Silver Abalone and Mother of Pearl
description:
Length: 1.75"

Alpaca silver pin from Mexico. This Hummingbird pin has an inlaid mother of pearl and Abalone and a locking bar pin closure.
100% Handmade in Mexico by the women belonging to the Art Camp cooperative.

Art Camp (Artesanas Campesinas) was created in 1970-s as a women-owned cooperative occupied with abalone jewelry production. It is a classic fashion jewelry product with the the tradition of fine Mexican jewelry present in every piece. View more work from Art Camp here: 
http://globein.com/artisan/art-camp#pane-user-items

name: Copper Pendant with Green Beads Necklace - India
description:
Height: 11.6", Weight: 0.35kg

Original, ethnic, and colorful.
Based in the heritage city of Hyderabad Indai, Hoi Cho is a family-run artisan craft shop. Focusing on traditional and folk Indian art, Hoi Cho delivers the crafts with rich Indian elements. 
Handmade copper pendant with small green glass beads and copper finish fiber beads. 
View more work from Hoi Cho here:
